  <brief_title>Early Metabolic Response in Locally Advanced Esophageal Cancer Undergoing Induction Chemoradiotherapy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Early Metabolic Response Evaluation With 18-FDG PET-CT in Esophageal Cancer Treated With Neoadjuvant Chemoradiotherapy Followed by Esophagectomy</official_title>
  <sponsors>
